I would say Dr Priya is a very professional, friendly *** ************* doctor. She deals with patients as they are her own family members and she has mastered the art of dentistry as she holds the experience of decades in this profession.

There is very less wait time as the appointments are scheduled on mutual availability for every patienys.

The clinic is well equipped with all the advanced tools and machineries and she is very much conscious about the sanitation.

The best part (whatt i feel) is the costs for the treatment is comparatively lower to other dentists in this city. 

So having said that i would personally recommend Dr. PRIYA to all the people out there,  just search on google,  get the direction n visit for any dental treatment.Its just opposite to Concorde Manhattan in Neeladri road. You can see the 'THE DENTIST' board over there..  

n trust me, you will be reviewing the same way as im doing right now! Thats for sure :) kudos!! 

Thankyou Dr Priya n hope you are doing good!!
Very friendly. Doctor explains everything so patiently *** *** ** *** **** ******* ** ******** Well equipped clinic and good suggestion of medicines

Dr. Priya is an excellent dentist. She took the time to explain every procedure she was doing. For example, when I got my Root Canal  Dr.Priya was very supportive, and thorough when explaining the process. She is a professional and has a naturally lovely personality. I would recommend Dr. Priya to everyone. *** ** *** **** ******* * **** **** ****I was absolutely petrified about having root canal. I got 1 beautiful crown done. They look so natural and the whole process was very smooth . She was so lovely and comforting. 
I recommend Dr. Priya efficient and caring and just great overall.

3 root canals 3 crown and the odd dental issues every now and then…
This is how my association with Dr Priya began. I have always found Dr Priya to be a very caring dentist, taking all her time to listen to the problem, explaining the cause and her course of treatment. 
It has been over 4 years since my 1st crown was implanted followed by a couple more. All of them have been very durable and haven’t caused any problems till now. And not to forget, hygiene is given paramount importance in her clinic.
From a patient to a Friend is how this has translated over these years.
Continue doing the good work, Dr Priya.

Dr. Priya is fine Doctor but then i m so satisfied with the service. We went to see her yesterday at 12 pm and she checked my father(patient). After examining she informed that treatment to be followed which all went well. She suggested to consult physician before extraction of the wisdom tooth. Agreed. We were finding it difficult to find the doctor address so we reached out to Practo to check on this and this was not my complaint. Today again we went to her with the physician report in the afternoon at 12 which was given to us 4 days back by Lal pathlab which we got done for the medical insurance and I asked her if she can check the same on mail and she told she don’t hv any issue in checking that but then she requested us to come at 4 pm as she was busy with patients. 
We went to see her at 4pm again and then she denied to check the report and we dont kn why.she 
also asked me why i complained abt her to practo which i feel is nt the good way of interacting with patients and she asked me to contact practo and talk about this. I wouldn’t recommend anyone to go there.
